{"tid":405981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撐獨媒都要禁？嶺大生貼標語抗議被撕","createTime":"2017-09-19T09:32:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-19T10:48:48.000Z","uid":39464,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"02d273e7c296a2d62c7415273725601e7121452f","tid":405981,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T09:32:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170919/large/1505808643_44f5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170919%2Flarge%2F1505808643_44f5.png&h=d4f1049a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嶺南大學民主牆再現港獨有關標語，當中唯「獨立」疑被人撕去。嶺大文化研究系二年級學生阿傑接受《蘋果》訪問，他於昨晚約10時在大學民主牆張貼「支持香港獨立媒體」標語，他表示此舉為語帶雙關，因標語既出現「香港獨立」四字，同樣亦可理解為支持香港獨立媒體（簡稱「獨媒」）。<br />\n<br />\n阿傑解釋，張貼標語是了對十大校長的聯署「反港獨」聲明表達不滿，昨晚張貼時有學生圍觀、亦有保安員同場，但沒有人出言阻止或表示不滿。不過，今早有同學經過民主牆時發現，標語中「獨立」兩字被撕去，只餘下「支持香港媒體」六個字。<br />\n<br />\n阿傑強調，張貼標語有跟足民主牆規定，包括有寫下學生編號及張貼日期，而民主牆上合規的標語，張貼期限為7天，他初步推斷有反對港獨的人士撕去標語，但無法完全排除由校方所撕除，「無論係邊個撕，都都極不尊重我嘅言論自由，如果唔同意的嘅觀點，大可以喺民主牆上留言辯論。」<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》正向嶺大校方查詢，目前等待回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57229601&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170919\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57229601%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170919&d=jWODVY9xXFwp0mmthCJ0jP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=8a3ceb4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57229601%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170919&h=b61762b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57229601&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170919</a>"},{"pid":"03824a5ebfa157c883bfc684936bf59259941c1f","tid":405981,"uid":90601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T09:36:54.000Z","msg":"獨立屋？<br />\n獨立樂隊？<br />\n獨立搖滾？<br />\n獨立品牌？<br />\n美國獨立宣言？<br />\n獨立財務顧問？"},{"pid":"835164d655c88138a9f36eda4b1ea2efc351377e","tid":405981,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T09:38:23.000Z","msg":"支那人咁唔想見到獨立去上海啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeecbf494a528f60af88b285fd004ab0d8d50819","tid":405981,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T09:45:01.000Z","msg":"我大個仔 想試下獨立"},{"pid":"47972386338af5fc52268e581fbba7c4da8c8258","tid":405981,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T09:54:09.000Z","msg":"上次撕野條支蛆仲未捉到?"},{"pid":"4668d21ac6ee52fec1e41d6384d807d6ffbaede6","tid":405981,"uid":12021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T09:54:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"de7be5bb346742bf0fbf990e38450607dcc13613","tid":405981,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T09:59:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲未拉到支那狗？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嶺大班人真係... <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9ca67ace166abf2d6df8e7013b4915ebbbfb40","tid":405981,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T10:46:54.000Z","msg":"《十年》情節終於出現"},{"pid":"50848cca09b721bbcbf37ebafcf1b6b30e0f25fa","tid":405981,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T10:48:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>《十年》情節終於出現</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f8508JAEP70\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Df8508JAEP70&d=jWODVY9xXFwp0mmthCJ0jP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=74a07e5a\" target=\"_blank\">https:/